{"tid":1076781,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[入嚟好唔好］呢個世界真係好L神奇","createTime":"2019-03-25T06:12:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T06:35:54.000Z","uid":243296,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a4a50f1599f868a2d3fe303aa2d975d75d5d0a06","tid":1076781,"uid":243296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T06:12:01.000Z","msg":"有個識一年幾嘅朋友，下稱A<br />\n<br />\n佢係個幾安靜嘅女仔平時唔多講嘢，近排同拍拖一年嘅男朋友咗分手<br />\n<br />\n原因係個男仔搵到一個比A有錢比A靚嘅女仔，呢件事係A發現。嗰陣時佢哋拍拖一年兼同居，啲嘢唔還返俾A不止仲要其實曾經打過我朋友仲揚言話po LIHKG 仲話咩見一次打一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />刷新我世界觀<br />\n<br />\n呢啲都係我約佢出嚟傾計問吓先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />A嗰時睇佢Ex個手機仲要發現..Ex約嗰個女仔出嚟個原因居然一樣咩抑鬱想自殺呀<br />\n條女又真係受喎<br />\n仲要個男仔唔係靚仔嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以拍拖睇人品真係好緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw..<br />\n我係識A嘅時候其實佢有另外一個男朋友<br />\n但係A同佢ExEx分手其實係因為佢而家個Ex<br />\nA&amp;ExEx都拍拖好耐兩年以上<br />\n男仔條件都好好，各方面都好，對佢都好好，不過就係捉得A太緊，控制慾太強，同埋佢屋企人覺得A襯唔到佢仔仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢哋分手嗰時就算我哋圈子唔係話太Close<br />\nBut嗰排佢EXEX分手搵唔到A，甚至通過其他方法去聯絡我哋問A嘅近況<br />\n最恐怖嘅事佢曾經同A講喜新厭舊會有報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地覺得報應係呢個世界真係存在嗎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正皮  呢個世界邊度有報應，有嘅話大把人死<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />負皮  呢啲係報應，係天嘅懲罰"},{"pid":"027d573dfa616c6f84dae9e22aa6ec2911d533f8","tid":1076781,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T06:14:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">😂🙈😂🙈</span>"},{"pid":"34974ce674e813f8be9fe753220d2075c2a2513f","tid":1076781,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T06:14:43.000Z","msg":"傻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大把人冇報應不知幾開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"917ec2e3f8c7a46861f8d1f6a14c42ed0c1f451a","tid":1076781,"uid":243296,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T06:22:57.000Z","msg":"事在人為，一定係一個個選擇堆砌出嚟嘅錯誤，所以我都覺得報應係唔存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe2c1a09c9a42fb8a2f4d03325beda4a728308d","tid":1076781,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T06:28:02.000Z","msg":"咁長點睇呀"},{"pid":"0585e49c3698ec8a3a85b43d8ae9d5b6e6845007","tid":1076781,"uid":59159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T06:35:54.000Z","msg":"兩三句就完嘅事樓煮打咁撚長 真係好L神奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}